body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, thank you for contacting Car Dealership Support. My name is Ronald Gonzales. May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Hello Ronald, my name is Virginia Patterson.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Virginia. To assist you better, may I ask for your date of birth?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, my date of birth is the seventh of May, nineteen ninety-two.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you. Could you also provide the last four digits of your social security number?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Of course, the last four digits are zero four five six.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for sharing that information, Virginia. Is there anything else you need assistance with today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: No, that's all for now. I feel relieved that my privacy concern is being addressed.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I'm glad to hear that, Virginia. Thank you for reaching out to us. If you have any more questions, feel free to contact us anytime. Have a great day!
